# Cloudflare Pages redirect rules.
# Files in public/ are copied verbatim into dist/ at build time, so this file
# lands at the root of the deployed output where Cloudflare Pages reads it.
#
# Canonical redirect: www subdomain -> apex domain (Requirement 12.2).
# HTTP->HTTPS, TLS, and asset compression are handled by the Cloudflare
# platform and do not need rules here (Requirements 10.3, 11.4, 12.3, 12.4).
https://www.iglidhima.com/* https://iglidhima.com/:splat 301
